Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這條項鍊收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要給別人看到比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不說\N婆婆也叫我不要隨便給別人看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，命妳等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，為什麼會跑來這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:00:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白公主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說她是真白公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王少校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是一場大騷動呢，學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀\N真是支棒極了的“舞蹈”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說…你似乎認識她？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛，她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問，學園長是\N這間乙HiME學園的大人物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，算是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是愛莉卡，夢宮愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我…進這間學園就讀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心悸動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿盈內心 開始散放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會如此不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日一定會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算中途受挫也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能踏出小小的一步 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嶄新的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位姊姊好棒又好帥\N第2話 穿梭在少女花園的疾風!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也想當
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我決定要當
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我在找媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽以前似乎也是乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的母親叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆在告訴我之前就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這麼喜歡我的“舞蹈”嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可愛的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是很累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然突然昏倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法\N今天就先由我們照顧她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子不太妥當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這次的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定有許多人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多話要問她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王少校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是什麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等於是妳的城堡啊，學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜姊姊早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好掃地喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天靜留姊姊\N跟怪物進行“舞鬥”了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“舞蹈”真的可以用來戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是Meister的靜留姊姊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有還有，還有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妮娜被關進反省室了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？騙人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呀然後呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的做了這種事？\N妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，巴呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是個好機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妮娜遭到處分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴就可以當上第一名了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜很優秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒辦法勝任第一名的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是無欲無求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，莉莉耶，那邊還有垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶，我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮依娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的飛機…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那女孩的GEM嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞女士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為珊瑚第一名的妳\N怎麼會做出這種事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未經允許使用舞鬥服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自與主人定下假契約
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是大問題喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情形以後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被父親討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啦？真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀，妳醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安，真白公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請起床，早上了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再給我睡5分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，請快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望公主\N能早點和乙HiME訂下契約呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝迎賓館
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我非得在\N這麼狹小的房間裡醒來不可？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狹小…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快悶死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本…本…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的城？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慘啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（站在內心的窗邊 命運的側臉）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（點亮守護夢想之光吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（星兒只是…）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會遲到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審議會？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那兩人的處置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會在會議上討論
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那些無禮者害我的城…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主妳是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從14年前的那件事情以來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國民們期盼已久的\N正統王位繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週就要舉辦即位典禮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有人並不樂見此事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據情報指出，昨天的怪物\N似乎也是這些人做的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果公主待在城裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該不會發生這種慘事才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此看來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最原始的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您認為出在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正統繼承人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真會說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也還不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位公主說不定是真貨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活過來了～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，吃飽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在衣服乾之前先委屈一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，請問…陽子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能當上乙HiME吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還咦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我拜託過學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還讓我睡在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看審議會的結果決定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審議會？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集許多國家的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討論關於學園的營運\N和乙HiME的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想也知道不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主，請不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫德布倫王國的下一任女王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白·布藍·杜·溫德布倫陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是公主耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟想像中的不太一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME可是跟像我這種\N身份高貴的人共有生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿榮譽的職業
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像妳這種小不點怎麼當得成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是小不點？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳給我慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太愉快了，我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託，請讓我參加審議會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想親自正式拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長要我看著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審議會是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擺一道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆也說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拼命拜託的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位，聽好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為一個乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論何時何地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在迎接主人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都必須拿出最高級的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，各位試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人，歡迎您回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人，歡迎您回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王，妳出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝審議會要審問妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒，好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽以前一定也是在這學習的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，目標是審議會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在哪裡舉行啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在開始進行\N加爾德羅貝審議會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前\N可以先討論一件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，妮娜真讓人擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我倒是覺得蠻愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀唉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米雅妳怎麼可以說這種話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們是朋友對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，詩帆姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:13:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效，有效耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本家流傳的傳說中\N“虎捲人偶”真有效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然拒絕負責我的房間\N妳還早一萬年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色捲捲藍色捲捲紅色捲捲…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想問個路…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找審議會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這裡的學生吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，應該說還不是呢\N還是說以後會是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是連妳一起捲捲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳給我慢著～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆姊姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了，有可疑人物入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請妳們追嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N聽說詩帆姊姊她們正在追
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷窺魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，聽說是女色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了，在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？內衣賊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的小姑娘，妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了，在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著～\N糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的小屁股看光光了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著\N喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，聽說校舍被入侵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是說那個可疑人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是像昨天的怪物一樣\N就有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依琳娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在真祖的引導之下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會馬上抓到可疑人物…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴獸出現，飛機起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬌嫣的紫水晶身為五柱之一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在未獲得審議會認可的情況下\N進行舞鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及風華宮的破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們希望能由相關當事人口中\N直接聽取說明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好像少了一位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日的議題跟這件事有關
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當事人之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊的妮娜是本校學生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一位叫做愛莉卡的少女\N則希望能入學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然算是特例…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能允許那位少女入學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，我在找審議會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審議會？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是說議事堂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那個，請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上哪去了～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀，是茱麗葉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:17:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就別叫我茱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，這麼一說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個阿爾泰的惡劣女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天要捲捲妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有議事堂的話，那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途入學？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有前例啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年有多少少女志願入學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻含淚而歸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信學園長非常清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生入學並不是\N妳一個人就可以決定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以擔保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫愛莉卡的少女\N擁有成為優秀乙HiME的資質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那邊的妮娜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也不打算處分妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:19:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這次的事件\N是為了保護真白公主的性命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是這個叫妮娜的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那個叫愛莉卡的無禮者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有資格成為乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，還沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“那邊”…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪裡啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣把她趕進議事堂裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是真白公主\N也不得推翻審議結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，真白公主說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要審視過乙HiME的力量\N與扮演的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案自然顯而易見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說，王少校\N您應該是當事者的義父
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽扯到利益關係的發言\N是不是該謹慎點？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:19:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託，請讓我進入這間學校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然停下來嘛\N很重耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們這是在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞女士，非常對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了\N快走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想應該不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過剛剛這位少女就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀，真是讓我看了場好戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，真白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下，您不是應該明天才會到？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想早一天\N殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到我心愛的真白呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一點也不想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是這麼不解風情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大公殿下，審議會還在進行…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致上的事情我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是那個\N想成為乙HiME的女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係，就讓她進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是阿爾泰大公殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能自作主張決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更遑論這次的問題\N關係到殿下國家的候補生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王的進退啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡言之殿下也是當事者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能夠控制一下發言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了當乙HiME的話\N什麼都能做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這麼辦如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以真白即位典禮餘興節目的名目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她跟妮娜比劃一場舞鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏的人可以留在學校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸的就離開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:21:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點子不賴吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:21:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大公殿下，這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我打
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她比劃一場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.11,0:22:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.38,0:23:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.77,0:23:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.17,0:23:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.11,0:23:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.79,0:23:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好驚訝，真白是公主呀\N（首·次·經·驗）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.43,0:23:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見面的時候\N還以為妳是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？我是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我檢查看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.34,0:23:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.27,0:23:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，真的都沒有耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管上面還是下面都…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,




